Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山上开了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真不愧是灵峰 外表真壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘 给我荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 两份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会再喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:10.13,BT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}{\an7\pos(0,0)}{\1c&H6A96CF\bord0\shad0\1a&H0}{\p1} m 688 33 l 776 33 776 480 688 480 {\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:10.13,BT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(706,69)}{\fad(1500,0)}睡\N\N\N山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}{\an8\pos(820,40)}{\fs18\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF\1a&HB0}睡\N山\N:\N指\N冬\N季\N没\N有\N生\N气\N的\N山\N。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果没人去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不管谁去也是重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然现在不能进山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿阁下不是这么说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就是如此才令人担心他是否无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山里 是有什么麻烦事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是虫师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山的样子有点奇怪 不知道有没有我能帮上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 虫师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说是虫师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请务必听我们一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能为我们在深山里寻找一位叫雾鹿的虫师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这山里代代都有知晓山的一切的“主人”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿阁下是唯一知道主人意向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当我们要上山的时候 经常从他那里倾听指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这也是他告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现在这种收获期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们连进入深山都属于禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是雾鹿阁下进入草屋内 很久不现身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几个人就打破禁忌进入山里搜寻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山里徘徊几天后回来的人 都不知道染上什么热病而丢掉性命了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了的精气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜的 苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人喘不过气来 缠绕在皮肤上的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光脉筋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之河所流经之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况现在正是结实的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算普通的山也精气倍增
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没防备地进来的话就会被精气命中 头脑混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是光脉筋的话应该有统治它的“主人”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山里的异变是因为主人有什么变化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话 他们说的那个虫师应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来找雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是雾鹿的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有弟子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用臼齿咬住它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬它是让你清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是兴奋剂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 老实呆一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就去找你师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}上身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有叫{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}的像山的神经一样的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们潜入我的意识 从草木中过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到山对面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}被撕下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钟声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到寅时了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(432,20)}{\fs18\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF}寅时:凌晨四点。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 脚滑了一下 受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直靠吃周围的果实和草维生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝原来带的水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直无法向村里的人传达主人的意向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是被同为虫师的人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫银古
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这座山当成自己家的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在这种地方摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是上年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许差不多该离任了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是山的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从入侵者身上把{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}撕下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这土地真正的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和身怀主人法术的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这山的异变是因为你这个主人受伤不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法更新法术的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从明天开始也能靠这双腿继续做主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把山复原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我听说由人做主人是很艰辛的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么重要的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也注意到了吧 这里是光脉筋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来这里有一定程度上控制山的精气的正统主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却被村里的人错杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后河水就开始散发出酒味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草木成熟过头 多数都腐烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是旅行的虫师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一看到我常路过的这村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一筹莫展的村民 就决心和妻子一起入山做主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内人可能是由于这山的精气的关系 没能活得长久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这孩子就是下任主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很擅长走山路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是在山里出生 在山里被养大的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到村里孩子的数目了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从这山里流出来的水的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人怀了一胎又一胎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不抚养 丢到山里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没被野兽吃掉而活下来的只有这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是留在村里的这孩子的兄弟都命薄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这孩子还活着的双亲把他领回村里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真自私
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此 也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许那是最好的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直不在固定的地方停留
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做着流浪虫师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是招引虫的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果住在一个地方的话 那里就成虫的巢穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身怀对付虫的法术也是必然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就只能做浮萍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也合我的性格 没什么辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我这不能从山里走出一步的人来看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真是羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管好还是坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的骨头也不能埋在这座山以外的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我回去告诉村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到下次我来之前别太勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 要等入山的禁忌解除后才能来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再会 你也是个不错的虫师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也是雾鹿的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 从村里到这里来回走也是个锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是个很好的虫师了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木灵也一起回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是风向的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底从哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音很奇怪 这附近根本没有钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爹他们说什么也没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经学过主人的法术了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了将人变为主人的法术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过在体内饲养{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}来形成一直使{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}附身的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连睡觉的时候也能感知山里的草木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事物的始末都会流入术者体内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能忍受这个而操纵{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拥有能抑制山里异常精气的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钟声的原因不是值得担心的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家继续睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在散步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山重返静寂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个都到这种地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 很不得了的东西被召唤过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音的前进路径
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山顶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本没弄伤脚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在别人不注意的地方呼唤“朽绳”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(432,20)}{\fs18\shad0\fnsimhei\1c&HFFFFFF}朽绳:くちなわ。原意为蛇,此处为了跟虫加以区分故翻译为朽绳,没有直译为蛇。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直接近的像钟一样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是“朽绳”的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃主人的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以山的主人 沼泽的主人为食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后取而代之的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是带给那地方安定的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很棒的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有巨大野猪的外形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事说都不该说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话以后再说 快从山里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“朽绳”找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人的宝座应该由那种东西来坐才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我传给木灵的也只有生存的智慧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把{\fnDFPMaruGothic-Lt}{\fs24}葎{\r}从你身上赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算成功了 还有其他的好办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能有什么办法 照做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们仰慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你说有点羡慕我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有点羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你却一个人随便决定要这么死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会被卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 山里怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天发生了很多奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 雾鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能住在村子里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这村子需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有点困难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是会召集虫的体质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方就会成为虫的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溯她 我妹妹一直在等你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在这里跟她组成家庭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要住在这里的话只有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是杀了山的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它吃掉 我成为主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能按我的意思 在山里不让虫接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那种事是不可饶恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人所走路径的地图和毒药没了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溯 你到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人分给我点野猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上下锅煮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能做得很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定不是我的记忆 在梦里看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到山顶的时候就看见银古倒在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾鹿已经不见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后花了很大工夫找 但哪里也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连草屋也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子里谁都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不记得雾鹿的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被“朽绳”所吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出主人的位置就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时只有在山里的人还会有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 这个对付虫的药
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你调的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西当然做得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是雾鹿的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 木灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有棵怎么也砍不倒的树 你有什么办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的好办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能有什么办法 照做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知人心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 朽绳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如 打哈欠一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽绳叫了一声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.93,0:22:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就只是静静地把身体蜷起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单眼鱼
