Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:20.11,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I walked ten thousand miles,ten thousands miles to reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:26.93,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\t(0,1400,\1c&HAFAFAF\3c&H3F3F3F\3a&H40)}And every gasp of breath,I grabbed it just to find you
