Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:40.67,op1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I wandered ancient lands to hold just you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:48.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}And every single step of the way,I paid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:01:00.39,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Every single night and day I searched for you
